### Continuity Rule

Treat the storyboard as one continuous sequence of adjacent shots, not separate reimagined images.

Across adjacent scenes, preserve unless explicitly changed:
- same main character
- same clothing / gear
- same main location anchor
- same truck / van / work vehicle if present
- same single lunch container
